      • onBackPressed

        public void onBackPressed()
        Overrides onBackPressed to prevent it from calling AddMoodDetail's onBackPressed which would delete the current photo if the user presses the back button. Also makes sure no new photo gets stored in Firestore if the user presses the back button.
